  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◎ UNI is a two-player party game containing 40 different types of mini games.</strong></h2><br>UNI includes games from many genres adapted for a two-player game experience:<br>(By update 2019/06/07 5 Games are added and New Mode (Random 5 mode) is added.<br>Sports, Action, Fighting, Arcade, Racing… Even RPG!<br>It’s easy to play and the rules are quite simple, making it enjoyable for all people regardless of age or gender.<br><br>With UNI, enjoy a happy and wonderful game experience together with your family, friends, and partners.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◎ Feature of UNI</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 mini games of various genres</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple rules for all ages</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cute game graphics and fancy screen effects and sound effects</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can play with one keyboard or two game controllers</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New free mini games will be added through update!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This game can be played by sharing one keyboard but for full enjoyment it’s better to use 2 joysticks. (recommended controller for Xbox)</strong></h2><br>In Keyboard Play Mode<br><br>Player 1 can play with<br>Q  W  E<br>A  S  D<br>Z  X  C<br>Keys.<br><br>Player 2 can play with<br>7  8  9<br>4  5  6<br>1  2  3<br>Keys.<br><br>OR<br><br>I  O  P<br>K  L  ;<br>,  .  /<br>keys in tenkeyless keyboard.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◎ UNI is a two-player party game containing 40 different types of mini games.</strong></h2><br>UNI includes games from many genres adapted for a two-player game experience:<br>(By update 2019/06/07 5 Games are added and New Mode (Random 5 mode) is added.<br>Sports, Action, Fighting, Arcade, Racing… Even RPG!<br>It’s easy to play and the rules are quite simple, making it enjoyable for all people regardless of age or gender.<br><br>With UNI, enjoy a happy and wonderful game experience together with your family, friends, and partners.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◎ Feature of UNI</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 mini games of various genres</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple rules for all ages</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cute game graphics and fancy screen effects and sound effects</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can play with one keyboard or two game controllers</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New free mini games will be added through update!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This game can be played by sharing one keyboard but for full enjoyment it’s better to use 2 joysticks. (recommended controller for Xbox)</strong></h2><br>In Keyboard Play Mode<br><br>Player 1 can play with<br>Q  W  E<br>A  S  D<br>Z  X  C<br>Keys.<br><br>Player 2 can play with<br>7  8  9<br>4  5  6<br>1  2  3<br>Keys.<br><br>OR<br><br>I  O  P<br>K  L  ;<br>,  .  /<br>keys in tenkeyless keyboard.",
